## Naming Conventions

| Thing | Convention | Example |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| Files | `snake_case.dart` | `goals_provider.dart` |
| Classes | `PascalCase` | `GoalsNotifier`, `GoalDetailScreen` |
| Providers | `camelCase + Provider` | `goalsProvider`, `claudeServiceProvider` |
| Notifier methods | `verbNoun` | `addGoal`, `toggleActive`, `recordSessionCompletion` |
| Private methods | `_verbNoun` | `_loadFromProfile`, `_persist` |
| Private widgets | `_PascalCase` | `_GoalTile`, `_SessionButton` |
| Screen widgets | `PascalCase + Screen` | `GoalDetailScreen` |
| Tab widgets | `PascalCase + Tab` | `AffirmationsTab` |
| Dashboard sub-widgets | in `features/dashboard/widgets/` | `AffirmationSessionCard` |

