## Code Quality Checklist

Before finishing any file:
- [ ] No hardcoded colors, spacing, or strings — use tokens and `AppStrings`
- [ ] No direct Firestore/Firebase calls in widgets or models
- [ ] Every `async` widget method has `if (!mounted) return` after awaits
- [ ] Every `fromJson` has null-safe fallbacks
- [ ] No `print()` — use `debugPrint()` with a context prefix
- [ ] No unused imports
- [ ] Private widgets extracted when they exceed ~40 lines or are reused
- [ ] `const` constructors used wherever possible
